features: Perfect For: Our medium bristle toothbrush is great for anyone who wants pain-free oral care and prefers bristles that are a bit harder but still not rough on your gums.
Effective Cleaning: Our toothbrush has Nollex bristles, which feature a rounded finish. They offer gentle yet thorough cleaning power, leaving your teeth, gums, and tongue squeaky clean.
Smart Shape: The handle of our brush is designed in a comfortable, ergonomic shape and while the head is short and rounded, it makes it easy to fit everywhere in your mouth.

Recommended Use: Brush your teeth twice a day, using your favorite toothpaste or tooth powder. It is important to replace your toothbrush every three months or after a cold or illness for the best dental care.
Prevent & Protect: Proper and regular teeth brushing can help remove plaque, prevent bad breath, and could help to stop periodontal disease and prevent gingivitis.
body.description: Are you looking for a cleaner mouth? Let Tello help you achieve just that. Our toothbrushes are designed for people who want a beautiful smile, and more importantly, for those who take their dental hygiene seriously. Our brushes feature a sleek handle which is not only attractive, but ergonomically designed to help you correctly brush your teeth. What sets our toothbrushes apart are the bristles. The Nollex bristles are very gentle thanks to the rounded tips, but offer extremely thorough and effective cleaning throughout the life of your brush. They are waterproof and fast drying which helps prevent decay and deform like you see with so many other toothbrushes. The compact head is smartly designed to reach every corner of your mouth, making sure you don’t miss a spot. If you’re looking to make the switch to a high-quality toothbrush that changes the way you brush your teeth, Tello is the answer.

reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars One that actually fits the standard bathroom holes!
reviews.reviewText: I use an electric toothbrush most of the time but I wanted to just have an extra one in the bathroom. And when I can grab to go somewhere overnight. My ADHD cannot handle the fact that no toothbrush fits in the standard holder. I live in an older rental. There's not a lot of sink area space and I'm kind of grossed out by toothpaste holders that are closed. It's soft and it's perfect!

reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Well made toothbrush!!
reviews.reviewText: I was interested in trying a different kind of toothbrush from the normal crest and colgate ones, so I gave this a shot. And I have to say I'm really glad I did. The first thing you notice is the curve of the toothbrush allows you to get good pressure for brushing as well as being able to reach the more hard to reach places in your mouth. The bristles also feel made of a higher quality and are a perfect medium. Overall highly recommended! Will be buying again!
